{"tid":1543611,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇到呢D後生仔  根本唔需要再考慮","createTime":"2019-09-05T08:55:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T10:30:15.000Z","uid":224992,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"76b5487a0236863999399193dbe2fe372fb6aff2","tid":1543611,"uid":224992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:55:37.000Z","msg":"大家要小心柒婆慣左口講一套  做另一套<br />\n尋晚太子旺角<span style=\"color: red;\">冇</span>直接衝去拉人<br />\n甚至有個差婆DJ扮溫柔<br />\n極有可能係扮斯文<br />\n忍你一兩日  之後再拉再打  比之前更甘<br />\n10月4日就區選報名<br />\n希望到時在抗爭攬炒之外(我認為絕不能停)   可以有認真討論  <br />\n五大訴求入面 其實冇包括到我地嘅焦點<br />\n到底我地個焦點係要針對:<br />\n1. 中央  <br />\n2. 中聯辦 <br />\n3. 黑警<br />\n如果區議非建議嬴  可以令市民得到D乜  我覺得到時有必要講下大勝<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkdinterview/videos/2779260362101840/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkdinterview%2Fvideos%2F2779260362101840%2F&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MNey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=c7e6eef2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkdinterview/videos/2779260362101840/</a><br />\n我年紀都唔細  但我好尊敬呢D後生仔 <br />\n為左你地  為左9條人命  幾隻眼 無數作出不同程度犧牲嘅人 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>五大訴求  <br />\n缺一不可</strong></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實winter on fire已經一步一步在香港重覆緊<br />\n係完全一模一樣<br />\n大家做定心理準備<br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"e6d0414b63003dfdb8363395338a88b3f537c14c","tid":1543611,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:55:48.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.